.: about :.

They call you Contract Jack-Just Another Contract Killer. 
You have a reputation for being able to solve problems, 
particularly in cases of questionable legality. 
But now you&#039;ve got problems of your own.

The legendary chief assassin for H.A.R.M. organization 
has given you a mission-whether you want it or not. 
An Italian criminal organization has plans to take H.A.R.M. 
down and you must stop them.

In doing so, you&#039;ll contend with the deadliest enemies you&#039;ve
seen and survive against ridiculous odds to complete your mission.
Intense firefights and cataclysmic predicaments are constant in this
exhilarating step forward for the No One Lives Forever franchise.
